name: Image Dictionary
body:
Image Dictionary is an open-source extension for Google Chrome browser which displays images corresponding to the selected text on the page.

![Image Dictionary](http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-_94FsQXeDxw/Uh779WYrR9I/AAAAAAAAAeg/VDnxyMz26nc/s1600/1.png)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
